{"tid":2048643,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"財新5月中國服務業PMI升至約9年半高位","createTime":"2020-06-03T02:52:39.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-03T02:52:39.000Z","uid":166360,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"2fabfb28cbf04a7c537c526a2de48ed2ac5149f2","tid":2048643,"uid":166360,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-03T02:52:39.000Z","msg":"財新5月中國服務業PMI升至約9年半高位<br />\n2020-06-03 HKT 10:24<br />\n<br />\n財新5月中國服務業採購經理指數(PMI)由4月的44.4大幅回升至55，是2月以來首次重返擴張區間，亦是約9年半高位。<br />\n<br />\n受內需回升，帶動上月服務業新訂單指數自2月以來重回擴張區，但新出口訂單指數仍處於收縮。<br />\n<br />\n財新智庫高級經濟學家王喆認為，<span style=\"color: blue;\">內地服務業從疫情中加速恢復，需求較製造業強。</span>他指，雖然供需按月有改善，但仍不能完全抵銷疫情的負面影響，預期經濟回復到常態仍需時日。<br />\n<br />\n另外，財新上月中國綜合PMI由4月的47.6回升至54.5，是約9年高位。 <br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1529899-20200603.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1529899-20200603.htm&d=9MYRmPDtC2YjWedq%2F%2Fxxger6kk4zB%2BnGw4DSdwpbM%2Bg%3D&h=fe13ce7d\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1529899-20200603.htm&h=1330bc29\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1529899-20200603.htm</a><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\"><br />\n厲害了，我的國</span></strong></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}